  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-EP-03 stale dataset)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification is performed. All 13 credibility factors are assessed; the package records Accepted based on stated achieved levels. A stale-data weakener is latent: the primary experimental dataset carries a dataVintage of 2018-03-15, predating the modelRevisionDate of 2026-01-10, and the narrative does not address re-validation against the revised model build.",
