    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 credibility factors assessed or flagged; Monte Carlo UQ completed across primary input uncertainties. Achieved levels fall below required levels for all assessed factors, consistent with the MRL 5 gap profile documented in the Morrison framework. The assessment team accepted the package as complete for submission purposes, noting that all identified gaps are documented. The primary experimental validation dataset (FDA inter-laboratory study, dataVintage 2018-03-15) was applied without re-validation against the current model build (modelRevisionDate 2026-01-10); the assessment narrative does not address whether model revisions since 2018 affect the applicability of the archived experimental reference data.",
